DeepStar: 30 → 90 → 27 → 90 → 24 → 100 → 24

**Statements:**

APPLICABLE: "BroadBand''s biggest problem is proportion who want to work there if successful"
→ 40 erreichen Application, nur 10 wollen wirklich dort arbeiten (25%)

