→ Siehe Preferred Employer Rate

NOT APPLICABLE: "DeepStar doesn''t do good job turning interested into employees"
→ DeepStar hat 100% Conversion von Application zu Preferred!

APPLICABLE: "DeepStar performs better in all dimensions"
